<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Proposal | Singapore Career Pathfinder</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <header class="site-header">
      <div class="container nav-bar">
        <a class="brand" href="/" aria-label="PATH AI home">
          <img class="brand-logo" src="/images/pathai-brand-logo.svg" alt="PATH AI logo" />
          <span>PATH AI</span>
        </a>
        <nav class="nav-links">
          <a href="/">Home</a>
          <a href="/about">About</a>
          <a href="/proposal">Proposal</a>
          <a class="nav-cta" href="https://t.me/SingaporeCareerPathfinder_bot" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Try Chatbot</a>
        </nav>
      </div>
    </header>

    <main class="page-content">
      <div class="container">
        <section class="content-card">
          <p class="eyebrow">Proposal summary</p>
          <h1>Singapore Career Pathfinder proposal</h1>

          <div class="proposal-section">
            <h2>Problem and Audience</h2>
            <p>Many students feel unsure about which careers fit their diploma, degree, interests, and skills. Our target audience is polytechnic and university students in Singapore who are preparing for internships or graduation.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="proposal-section">
            <h2>AI Solution</h2>
            <p>We propose an AI chatbot that asks a few simple questions and then recommends career paths, possible job roles, salary guidance, and employer expectations.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="proposal-section">
            <h2>Project Objectives</h2>
            <p>The project aims to make career guidance easier, more personalised, and more useful for students who need direction.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="proposal-section">
            <h2>Expected Value</h2>
            <p>Students can use the chatbot to understand their strengths, compare career ideas, and feel more confident about their next steps.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="proposal-section">
            <h2>Team Roles</h2>
            <p>Team 3 is responsible for planning the chatbot idea, preparing the content, and building the website and proposal materials.</p>
          </div>
        </section>
      </div>
    </main>

    <footer class="site-footer">
      <div class="container footer-content">
        <p>Singapore Career Pathfinder | Team 3</p>
      </div>
    </footer>

    <script src="/js/script.js"></script>
